name: P.W.33
description:
Animated GIF of P.W.33 smoking on set of filming the short film 'False Negative' directed by Samuel Walker. The short was written for a local sc-fi film festival and was made a few months before 2020 lockdown. The message the film held became more relevant as 2020 progressed.
To watch False Negative visit:
https://youtu.be/3KRwvNBkiQA
